{"tid":1394772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭雲（公民記者，被義務律師幫過）既澄清","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:14:09.000Z","uid":101888,"like":407,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"9aa6d131ed6ba14274cc4dd7e56d314db7b05a0d","tid":1394772,"uid":101888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1393439560794985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100003868649005%2Fposts%2F1393439560794985&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIESHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=a84747ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100003868649005/posts/1393439560794985</a><br />\n<br />\n澄清<br />\n有見網上一些爭論，作為過來人認為應該澄清。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n一、保釋金要自己畀。。。<br />\n在下一直習慣保釋金要自己畀，當事人可以和警署拗。<br />\n若在坊間找律師，已經需要計時間畀律師費，市價以萬計。但義務律師團隊通宵穿梭不同警署，協助保釋上庭，處理警暴投訴，一直不收分毫。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n二、義務律師團隊唔會跟到底。。。<br />\n在傘運被捕者有數百人，包括不同派系，凡在下所認識義務律師團隊都跟到底。<br />\n不解為何有人這樣造謠，是出於什麼惡意。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n三、叫你申請法援，即係律師團隊有錢收喇。。。<br />\n似乎有些人不明白，律師團隊要幫被告打甩官司，每名被告背後不止有一位大律師，背後還有一支律師團隊，只計睇警方錄影同辯方錄影，就要反覆睇幾個月，睇到佢地幾乎眼盲。<br />\n只要旁聽過梁天琦案，便知審訊牽涉幾多影片，辯方要同控方逐條片，每分鐘計時計秒咁拗。當然仲有法例同法律理據。<br />\n官司長達幾年，成支協助被告嘅律師團隊都要生活。若被告不幸不合資格申請法援，就要 claim 基金嘅錢，但基金嘅錢好有限，所以合資格申請法援都應該申請，以減輕基金負擔。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n四、暴動案勝算唔大。。。<br />\n視乎去區域法院抑或高等法院，後者有陪審團勝算較高。但去哪所法院完全由律政司決定，連法官都無權置喙。<br />\n而且案件性質因人而異。例如旺角衝突中有些被告的確做過嘢，警方影片拍得清楚，律師團隊建議認罪，致力於陳情和減刑，絕不表示他們做得差。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n五、律師團隊表現參差。。。<br />\n若果你住半山，請得到余若海同清洪，你可以咁講。<br />\n若果你是普通人，在下可以好肯定同你講：你通過基金搵到嘅律師一定比坊間好。<br />\n在下於區域法院見證過不同的暴動罪被告，通過基金或自行聘請律師，郭憬憲為前者服務，表現高下立判。<br />\n通過基金找到的大律師，比如李柱銘、駱應淦、潘熙、劉偉聰、郭憬憲等等，平時幫達官貴人打甩官司好搵好多，一般人根本請唔起；在律師行跟他們的徒弟也是全港最 top 嘅律師。<br />\n律師之間有佢地嘅恩怨，但好慶幸在下冇遇到。<br />\n＊ ＊ ＊<br />\n六、直接捐錢畀被告。。。<br />\n捐錢畀被告同捐錢畀基金冇衝突，正如買飯同買豬嘴可以並行不悖。<br />\n除非有人捐錢畀被告，多到能夠幫被告請清洪，否則在下真誠建議所有被告，都通過 612 基金求助，真的對他們最好，在下作為過來人出自肺腑。<br />\n不篤灰、不割蓆、不譴責。在下一直做到。<br />\n不要出於惡意分化就好。"},{"pid":"f22194a5fe86649a90584e32fbb4b75dffac25dc","tid":1394772,"uid":70973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"澄清POST推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2892a2bb133ccfad0724c322740014ac174515","tid":1394772,"uid":199553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe3337fddda7a2b0045f6357b1207f23ade163b8","tid":1394772,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"00d87cb455a534afdcaf42cc890ee63a5e6b4b65","tid":1394772,"uid":278434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n助推"},{"pid":"bf0af738d39a85befc865b75d51dd4785819c913","tid":1394772,"uid":273803,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n<br />\n45個義士一上庭，即刻就有大量抹黑612基金嘅post。根本好多律師都係又幫星火，又幫612。"},{"pid":"9fecfe210dcc5e46aca4809f021b13386a2259e8","tid":1394772,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"351aeaf2afc9925d5fffd57da529a8dbe9731bef","tid":1394772,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"懇請各大公司容許員工8月5號Home Office/ 彈性上班<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"736cb42f1ea775bbc0025596fb3ae0807c0d6c93","tid":1394772,"uid":101888,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"bf0af738d39a85befc865b75d51dd4785819c913","tid":1394772,"uid":273803,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n<br />\n45個義士一上庭，即刻就有大量抹黑612基金嘅post。根本好多律師都係又幫星火，又幫612。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"跟本幫義士既一直都係同一批律師"},{"pid":"5c1991be9cf19f53c9a34c88c68a2228b11522fd","tid":1394772,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d9182f044842dc220bde4c023537440ca84cdb4","tid":1394772,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11960c2ff93f3082a923f8881450846544efa52a","tid":1394772,"uid":160637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:11:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55923826a6ac760f76bb1be63682c3beaff5346b","tid":1394772,"uid":203889,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"bf0af738d39a85befc865b75d51dd4785819c913","tid":1394772,"uid":273803,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n<br />\n45個義士一上庭，即刻就有大量抹黑612基金嘅post。根本好多律師都係又幫星火，又幫612。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"[突發] 魚蛋義士親友對義務律師嘅睇法<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/jBLKFOX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/jBLKFOX</a><br />\n#361 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n#361<br />\n<blockquote>我係728被捕既其中之一位，現時正面臨暴動罪既起訴<br />\n覺得實在有責任係呢個時候出一出聲而不得不借一借朋友account<br />\n首先大家講關於義務律師既質素<br />\n幫我手果位義務律司係我入警署到我離開後，不論係對我法律上定個人問題上既支援都十分足夠，亦絕對超出一位律師應該要做既範圍以外，我唔敢幫其他手足發現，但對於一直幫我果位對義務律師，我十分十分感激，至於其他義務律師既質素我唔知所以不能評價，但我果位律師話我知，有好多個義務律師都係唔會按市價收612基金錢<br />\n而另外，對於612基金既質疑，今朝我聽到謠言話可能不足以應付全部法律開支都有擔心，所以直接打左去612果度問，聽電話果位十分詳盡地話我知，612基金係所有手足既司法案件完結之前，都會支付其所有法律開支，只不過，假如我地有手足符合法援資格，都建議申請，其實係相當合理，我既理解係，始終唔知未來仲會有幾多位手足被捕，如果能夠慳到啲錢幫更多既手足咁點解唔做？<br />\n現時對於612基金既質疑，我恐怕到最後只會令捐款減少，然後只會搞鳩到被捕手足，所以希望係呢個時候講多少少實際情況比大家知去辟謠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3joSnL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3joSnL.png&h=3f3bbec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n諗左好耐有咩文件可以證明自己身分，但發現全部都會自爆，唯有post一post呢半張，望各位信任我講既無半句假話</blockquote>"},{"pid":"46467222034b844af33b7f5dca2295c30bcb6fe0","tid":1394772,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:12:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"384f00d376df17033efa324cd021f9db4aa5f6cd","tid":1394772,"uid":236414,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"四、<span style=\"color: red;\">暴動案勝算唔大</span>。。。<br />\n視乎去區域法院抑或高等法院，後者有陪審團勝算較高。<span style=\"color: red;\">但去哪所法院完全由律政司決定</span>，連法官都無權置喙。<br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺得有話錯"},{"pid":"8ee1ca36a8a9c3bdcc4b5702977828b3474d79c9","tid":1394772,"uid":247082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:13:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d4579822bfce1645224282c39426dea4ee9e14","tid":1394772,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94040aa1c9c7c28371249f6d8cef4fcb807691b7","tid":1394772,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"402f5199d9cc7513b7c8d17a0d0c8c1ace2180ad","tid":1394772,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:14:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6b1a3ef3e7acd4f61b237149e7828ff6ef29014","tid":1394772,"uid":210031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39e71eacc92681285b6c7b70b4c5b2aa4bec89db","tid":1394772,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「救人！」世紀最大一人一Email 夾公務員罷工行動 第二波<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1394757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1394757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79f38bd9dcf15d2f26e9ba2e1f560001c58cbfd0","tid":1394772,"uid":119017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:14:53.000Z"